column5: Hello I just moved to the Barrie and I'm a big walleye fan from upnorth , just wondering where to find them around this area, I just have a 14ft aluminum boat, thanks

If you tell us a bit about yourself as a way of introduction, we would  be happy to help. I do not know very much about walleye so I am not a good resource. Welcome to the board.      PS: We LOVE pics.
jig and a grub?  works for me, mind you I haven't fished there before.  Oh and what HTHM said DOES go a LOOONG way too.
Where is up North and why would you ever move South?  This board is a wealth of knowedge and some members from that area will be sure to help you out.
